      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.501</ph> Applicability.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d709e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d736e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> This subpart applies to any contract
or subcontract at any tier for the acquisition of <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial products or
commercial services.<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.501 by removing from paragraphs (a) and (b) the term “commercial items” and adding “commercial products or commercial services” in its place.?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d736e19" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Nothing
in this subpart shall be construed to authorize the waiver of any
provision of law with respect to any subcontract if the prime contractor
is reselling or distributing <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial
products or commercial services<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.501 by removing from paragraphs (a) and (b) the term “commercial items” and adding “commercial products or commercial services” in its place.?></ph> of another contractor without
adding value. This limitation is intended to preclude establishment
of unusual contractual arrangements solely for the purpose of Government
sales.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d736e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> For purposes
of this subpart, contractors awarded subcontracts under <xref href="Subpart_19.8.dita#FAR_Subpart_19_8"
                        base="i1099848"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  19.8</xref>, Contracting
with the Small Business Administration (the 8(a) Program), shall
be considered prime contractors.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
